==English==
===Etymology===
from French, See [[Bolis]]

===Pronunciation===
IPA: [[WEAE]] /ˈbo.laɪd/ or /-lɪd/

===Noun===
'''bolide'''

# Any [[extraterrestrial]] body that collides with Earth
# An extremely bright [[meteor]]
# A [[fireball]]

====Quotations====
<BLOCKQUOTE>
The smallest impactor that can penetrate the atmosphere deep enough to cause any damage on the ground is not much smaller than the "Tunguska" bolide that flattened a couple thousand square miles of Siberian forest in 1908.<BR>
&mdash;''Alan Harris''
</BLOCKQUOTE>

